Extended Ace editor

This is actually ace editor ( http://ace.ajax.org/ ) in which we added toolbar with editor.
No need to manually write code for changing mode(syntax) , chainging theme changing font etc.
When ace editor is embeded in web page a tool bar come with editor,

Tool bar has buttons for open new File , fullscreen , change mode(syntax), change theme, change font, word wrpa toggle and help ,
We also add a functionality to toogle editor between textarea and editor.


See demo:

http://202.141.152.1/parikshak/ace_editor.html
